title: [1508521049] Welcome to the Channel - Gordon Ramsay
description:
As we come to the end of the year, just wanted to introduce you to the channel - and remind you to subscribe for weekly videos. If you're subscribed already, thanks for all the support. Let us know if there is anything you would like to see in 2014!

Click annotation or subscribe button and check the channel for over 300 videos.
